Name: Evil Superhero VR
About the game: This game world is massive, and includes: A large open world with a procedural environment, an entire ocean, Airplanes you can laser out of the sky... Unlimited Enemies you can Slice to bits with your Laser Vision, cars you can blow to pieces, and a Procedural AI Dismemberment System implemented into almost every NPC. So you can slice up and kill almost ANYONE in this game: civilian and enemy alike! Whether by accident or choice... It's up to you! You can also fly at Supersonic speeds through the world. No one can escape you once you've set your sights on them. You are Superhuman. And you can do whatever the f*** you want. Prepared to have the most fun in VR that you have ever experienced!!! Powers include: Sustained Supersonic Flight Laser Vision - with AI Procedural Dismemberment System for lasering enemies limb from limb Super strength Superhero Landing
